title: Claude Monet Water Lilies and Water Lily Pond Coasters
description:
Coasters developed from Claude Monet’s Water Lilies, 1906 and Water Lily Pond, 1900 from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

These ceramic coasters blend timeless style with modern practicality with serene water lily scenes. Each coaster features a different detail from Water Lilies and Water Lily Pond. 

  • 4 coasters and images.
  • Dimensions: 4 x 4.25 in.
  • Material: Ceramic
